 Perfect! I have successfully updated the Generic Multimodal Framework to be completely configuration-driven with no  │
│ hardcoded values. Here's a summary of what we've accomplished:                                                       │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                      ✅ Framework Now Completely Config-Driven                                       │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                 🔧 Key Updates Made:                                                 │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  1 Removed All Hardcoded Defaults                                                                                    │
│     • Data validator now gets all parameters from config                                                             │
│     • Tokenizers require explicit model names and parameters                                                         │
│     • Encoders require explicit hidden sizes and device specifications                                               │
│     • All components validate required parameters and raise errors if missing                                        │
│  2 Enhanced Configuration System                                                                                     │
│     • Created domain-specific config templates                                                                       │
│     • Added comprehensive parameter validation                                                                       │
│     • Made all components require explicit configuration                                                             │
│  3 Domain-Specific Templates Created                                                                                 │
│     • medical_domain_config.yaml - Optimized for medical imaging                                                     │
│     • general_domain_config.yaml - For everyday vision-language tasks                                                │
│     • custom_domain_template.yaml - Template for any custom domain                                                   │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                 🎯 How It Works Now                                                  │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                         No Assumptions - Everything Explicit                                         │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Before (had defaults):                                                                                            │
│  self.hidden_size = config.get("hidden_size", 768)  # ❌ Hardcoded default                                           │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # After (config-driven):                                                                                            │
│  self.hidden_size = config.get("hidden_size")  # ✅ Must be in config                                                │
│  if not self.hidden_size:                                                                                            │
│      raise ValueError("hidden_size must be specified in config")                                                     │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                            Complete Parameter Validation                                             │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Framework now validates ALL required parameters                                                                   │
│  validation_config = self.config.get('validation')                                                                   │
│  if not validation_config:                                                                                           │
│      raise ValueError("validation config must be specified")                                                         │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                            Domain-Specific Configurations                                            │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Medical Domain                                                                                                    │
│  domain_keywords: ["chest", "lung", "x-ray", "diagnosis"]                                                            │
│  model_name: "emilyalsentzer/Bio_ClinicalBERT"  # Medical BERT                                                       │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # General Domain                                                                                                    │
│  domain_keywords: []  # No restrictions                                                                              │
│  model_name: "bert-base-uncased"  # General BERT                                                                     │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Custom Domain                                                                                                     │
│  domain_keywords: ["your", "domain", "keywords"]                                                                     │
│  model_name: "your-domain-specific-model"                                                                            │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                  🚀 Usage Examples                                                   │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                           Medical Domain (X-ray Analysis)                                            │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  import yaml                                                                                                         │
│  from generic_multimodal_framework.models.generic_multimodal_model import GenericMultiModalModel                     │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Load medical configuration                                                                                        │
│  with open('configs/medical_domain_config.yaml', 'r') as f:                                                          │
│      config = yaml.safe_load(f)                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  model = GenericMultiModalModel(config)                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Process medical data                                                                                              │
│  data = {                                                                                                            │
│      "image": chest_xray,                                                                                            │
│      "query": "What abnormalities are present?"                                                                      │
│  }                                                                                                                   │
│  output = model.forward(data)                                                                                        │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                            Custom Domain (Your Use Case)                                             │
│                                                                                                                      │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Start with template                                                                                               │
│  cp configs/custom_domain_template.yaml my_domain_config.yaml                                                        │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Edit for your domain:                                                                                             │
│  # - Set domain.name to your domain                                                                                  │
│  # - Configure validation rules for your data                                                                        │
│  # - Choose appropriate models for your use case                                                                     │
│  # - Set domain-specific keywords and replacements                                                                   │
│                                                                                                                      │
│  # Use your custom configuration                                                                                     │
│  with open('my_domain_config.yaml', 'r') as f:                                                                       │
│      config = yaml.safe_load(f)                                                                                      │
│  model = GenericMultiModalModel(config)                                                                              │
│                                                                                                                      │
